{ //Gus

  //Gus Gift Tastes
  "CDE_Gus_GoldPumpkin": "Now THIS is something I'm curious to experiment with in the kitchen! Ho ho! The possibilities!$h",
  "CDE_Gus_RockCandy": "Look at the size of those crystals! I make good sweets, but I don't think I've ever seen one this perfect!",
  "CDE_Gus_Pearl": "That's a beauty of a pearl. I bet the oyster that made it would taste great, too!$h",
  "CDE_Gus_PrismaticShard": "What do we have here? Rainbow sherbet?#$b#Oho! Even better! A decorative stone that looks just like rainbow sherbet! And it'll never melt!$h",
  "CDE_Gus_Diamond": "This is fancy! What a beautiful little treasure.#$b#It's beyond generous, @. I'm speechless!",
  "CDE_Gus_Escargot": "Looks like you understand mature tastes! Well done, @, well done.#$b#I'm going to enjoy this plenty. Thank you very much.",
  "CDE_Gus_FishTaco": "Now this just can't be beat! That fish, that fried batter, that sauce, and that crunchy cabbage... it's got it all! Well done!",
  "CDE_Gus_Orange": "Goodness! You brought me one of my favorites? Thank you!#$b#Fresh orange juice, here I come.",
  "CDE_Gus_TropicalCurry": "Oh-ho! Looks like you put that tropical curry recipe to use! *slurp*#$b#Yep! Couldn't have made it better myself!$h",

  //Gus's Misc Dialogue
  //these lines target files other than the standard characters/dialogue/Gus location such as unmarried rainy dialogue
